<text top="82" left="83" width="450" height="54" font="1">Topic Learning Goals</text>
<text top="185" left="83" width="885" height="40" font="2">What key assumption must we make when transferring </text>
<text top="228" left="83" width="823" height="40" font="2">data between two secure terminals over a network?</text>
<text top="315" left="83" width="811" height="40" font="2">What vulnerability do we need to address with any </text>
<text top="358" left="83" width="186" height="40" font="2">encryption?</text>
<text top="444" left="83" width="867" height="40" font="2">What is Kerchkoffs’s principle and why is it superior to </text>
<text top="488" left="83" width="430" height="40" font="2">security through obscurity?</text>
