<text top="82" left="83" width="413" height="54" font="1">Frequency analysis</text>
<text top="404" left="53" width="965" height="34" font="4">The Man in the Middle views all our messages and knows that letters do </text>
<text top="440" left="53" width="937" height="34" font="4">not get used randomly, in any sufficiently long message this histogram </text>
<text top="476" left="53" width="798" height="34" font="4">will reveal the link between code letters and message letters</text>
<text top="512" left="53" width="902" height="34" font="4">• Side note, you should be able to apply this to wheel of fortune or </text>
<text top="548" left="94" width="125" height="34" font="4">hangman</text>
</page>
<page number="9" position="absolute" top="0" left="0" height="810" width="1080">
